msgctxt "92_Tanimura"
msgid "Hello?"
msgstr "Oi."

msgctxt "104_Anonymous Caller"
msgid "Tanimura-san, right?"
msgstr "Tanimura-san, right?"

msgctxt "116_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, that's me. And you are?"
msgstr "Yeah, that's me. And you are?"

msgctxt "128_Anonymous Caller"
msgid "Heh, that's not important. Let's just cut to the chase."
msgstr "Heh, that's not important. Let's just cut to the chase."

msgctxt "140_Anonymous Caller"
msgid "You want info on Katsuragi, don't you?"
msgstr "You want info on Katsuragi, don't you?"

msgctxt "152_Tanimura"
msgid "How did you...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo supiste...?"

msgctxt "164_Anonymous Caller"
msgid "It's my job to know that sort of thing. As such, it works only to my benefit to funnel information to you."
msgstr "It's my job to know that sort of thing. As such, it works only to my benefit to funnel information to you."

msgctxt "176_Tanimura"
msgid "That's... fine, but why should I believe some random caller who could be a total scammer for all I know?"
msgstr "That's... fine, but why should I believe some random caller who could be a total scammer for all I know?"

msgctxt "188_Anonymous Caller"
msgid "Good point. Except... You don't have anywhere else to turn right now, do you?"
msgstr "Good point. Except... You don't have anywhere else to turn right now, do you?"

msgctxt "200_Tanimura"
msgid "...Not really."
msgstr "...Not really."

msgctxt "212_Anonymous Caller"
msgid "That's what I thought. Now do you want that information or not? Of course, you could always hang up and be on your way."
msgstr "That's what I thought. Now do you want that information or not? Of course, you could always hang up and be on your way."

msgctxt "224_Tanimura"
msgid "No, let's hear what you have to say."
msgstr "No, let's hear what you have to say."

msgctxt "236_Anonymous Caller"
msgid "Smart man. Only thing is, nothing in life is free."
msgstr "Smart man. Only thing is, nothing in life is free."

msgctxt "248_Tanimura"
msgid "What, you're giving me a quote already?"
msgstr "What, you're giving me a quote already?"

msgctxt "260_Anonymous Caller"
msgid "Everything has its price, officer. But I'm not interested in your money. I just want to see how good of a detective you are."
msgstr "Everything has its price, officer. But I'm not interested in your money. I just want to see how good of a detective you are."

msgctxt "272_Anonymous Caller"
msgid "You'll be receiving a message from me shortly. Open it up, read it, and follow the instructions. Very self-explanatory."
msgstr "You'll be receiving a message from me shortly. Open it up, read it, and follow the instructions. Very self-explanatory."

msgctxt "284_Anonymous Caller"
msgid "Well, best of luck."
msgstr "Well, best of luck."

msgctxt "296_Tanimura"
msgid "Hey, we're not done yet!"
msgstr "Hey, we're not done yet!"

